After processing the 36 selected articles using descriptive
techniques, the analysis will focus on extracting key insights
and patterns related to integrating blockchain and generative
AI in educational data management.
The initial search covered several bibliographic repositories,
including IEEE Xplore, Science Direct, ProQuest, and Google
Scholar. The search was conducted in November 2023 and
included articles published between November 2018 and
January 2024. A total of 1,139 results met the search criteria.
