the main inclusion/exclusion criteria. This filtering stage has
a 2 step filtering process. First, we read the title, abstract, and
keywords, and then we discarded articles that were excluded
from inclusion. The second step is the reading process. We
read the contents of the articles thoroughly to find papers to
review. The final number of articles in the review process was
